      "Gorgeous mid-century modern sofa with a solid walnut frame and olive green cushions. This is a quality piece — not the cheap knockoff stuff you see everywhere.\n\n1. Solid walnut frame with tapered legs\n2. High-density foam cushions with removable covers\n3. 78 inches wide — seats 3 comfortably\n4. Cushions have been professionally cleaned\n5. No structural issues — frame is solid\n\nMoving to a smaller place and it just won't fit. This would cost $1,800+ new from a mid-century retailer.",
