      "Pottery Barn Samantha 3-Shelf Bookcase in Simply White. A timeless piece that works in a living room, office, or bedroom.\n\n1. Solid poplar and engineered wood construction\n2. Three fixed shelves plus the top surface\n3. Bead-board backing adds a nice cottage feel\n4. 46.5\"H x 42\"W x 14\"D\n5. Anchoring hardware included for wall safety\n\nWe redecorated and went in a different direction. This bookshelf is in excellent condition — no chips in the paint, no wobbly shelves. Retails for $699.",
      "Custom floating TV console in walnut, 72 inches wide. Wall-mounted design that makes your TV setup look incredibly clean.\n\n• Solid walnut face with hidden piano-hinge compartments\n• Two sections open to reveal storage for components\n• Cable management cutouts in the back\n• Soft-close hinges on all doors\n• Professional wall-mount hardware included\n\nHad this custom built by a local woodworker for $900. Selling because we're moving and the new living room layout doesn't work with a wall-mounted console.",
      "6-piece outdoor patio furniture set. Includes a 4-person sofa, 2 armchairs, a coffee table, and 2 side tables. Frame is powder-coated aluminum with all-weather wicker.\n\n1. Cushions are Sunbrella fabric — UV and water resistant\n2. Aluminum frame won't rust\n3. Wicker is synthetic PE rattan — holds up in any weather\n4. Cushion covers are removable and washable\n5. Coffee table has tempered glass top\n\nUsed for two summers on a covered patio. Everything is in great shape. This set was $1,400 new from Wayfair.",
      "Babyletto Hudson 3-in-1 convertible crib in white plus a matching changing table/dresser combo. Both pieces are in like-new condition.\n\nThe crib converts from crib to toddler bed to daybed — so it grows with your child. Greenguard Gold certified for low chemical emissions. The changing table has 3 spacious drawers underneath. Toddler rail conversion kit is included. Our little one graduated to a big kid bed. Non-smoking, pet-free home.",
      "Large L-shaped sectional sofa in grey linen fabric. This is a seriously comfortable couch — deep seats and soft back cushions.\n\n• Overall dimensions: 110\" x 85\" (L-shape)\n• Reversible chaise — configure left or right\n• Seat depth is 24 inches — great for lounging\n• Solid wood frame with sinuous spring support\n• All cushion covers are removable for washing\n• Includes 4 accent pillows\n\nWe've had this for about a year. No stains, no pet damage, no sagging. Just need something smaller for our new apartment.",
      "Set of 3 counter-height bar stools with solid wood seats and black metal frames. Seat height is 26 inches — perfect for standard kitchen counters and islands.\n\n1. Solid rubberwood seats with a natural finish\n2. Sturdy steel frame with footrest\n3. Protective floor pads pre-installed\n4. Each stool weighs about 12 lbs — easy to move\n5. 300 lb weight capacity per stool\n\nThese look great and are surprisingly comfortable even without cushions. Selling because we replaced our island with a lower dining table.",
