      "2022 Trek Marlin 7 mountain bike in Matte Nautical Navy. Size Large — fits riders 5'10\" to 6'2\". This bike handles trails and daily riding equally well.\n\n1. RockShox Judy fork with 100mm travel and lockout\n2. Shimano Deore 1x10 drivetrain — smooth and reliable\n3. Hydraulic disc brakes for confident stopping\n4. Tubeless-ready rims — currently set up with tubes\n5. Internal cable routing for a clean look\n\nRidden about 20 times on moderate trails and commuting. Tires have plenty of tread. Chain and cassette are barely worn. Recently tuned up at the local bike shop.",
