      "REI Co-op Half Dome SL 4-person backpacking tent. Three-season tent that's spacious enough for 4 but packable enough for the trail.\n\n• 2 doors and 2 vestibules for easy entry and gear storage\n• Full mesh body for ventilation — handles condensation well\n• Color-coded poles and clips make setup a 10-minute job\n• Floor area is 58 sq ft — actually fits 4 sleeping pads\n• Packed weight is 5 lbs 14 oz\n• Includes footprint (ground cloth)\n\nUsed on about 8 camping trips over two seasons. Seam-sealed from factory. No tears, no broken poles, all zippers work. Washed and dried per REI instructions.",
