      "Custom complete skateboard built with quality components. This isn't a Walmart board — it rides like a proper setup.\n\nBaker 8.25\" deck with fresh grip tape. Independent Stage 11 trucks — the industry standard. Spitfire Formula Four 53mm wheels — fast and flat-spot resistant. Bones Reds bearings. Deck has some tail wear and graphic scuffing from normal skating but structurally it's solid. Trucks are dialed in and wheels spin freely. Great board for street skating, park, or just cruising.",
      "2021 Specialized Tarmac SL6 carbon road bike, size 56cm. Full Shimano Ultegra R8000 groupset.\n\n1. FACT 9r carbon frame — stiff, light, and responsive\n2. Shimano Ultegra mechanical shifting — 22-speed\n3. Ultegra hydraulic disc brakes — powerful and modular\n4. DT Swiss R470 wheelset with 28mm Turbo Pro tires\n5. Carbon seatpost and Specialized Power saddle\n6. Weight is approximately 18.5 lbs as built\n\nAbout 2,500 miles on this bike. Chain and cassette were replaced at 2,000 miles. Frame is clean — no crashes, no cracks, no dents. Recent full tune-up. This bike retails for $3,500+ new.",
