      "LEGO Star Wars Millennium Falcon set #75192. This is the big one - the Ultimate Collector Series edition with 7,541 pieces. Fully assembled and displayed in a glass cabinet since the day I built it.\n\n• 100% complete - every piece accounted for\n• Includes all minifigures (both classic and Episode VII crews)\n• Original box and instruction booklets included\n• No yellowing or dust damage\n• Sticker sheet was applied perfectly\n\nRetails for $850+ and is frequently out of stock. Price is firm.",
